Assets.Name: KAP686_Cologne_V2_NoBarriers
Assets.Description:
KAP686 Skate Plaza - Cologne, Germany
I recommend playing this map with the time set to night at least once.
Thank you to everyone who helped me make this map ❤️ 

Last updated: Version 2.1 on 21.03.2023 | 03/21/23
When updating to a newer version delete the old one first or else some objects might look weird.
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1n4Tfse-d-b2Bx-kt8kS9HBn9eDqOqq-n/view02/24/2023: Initial Release
03/08/2023: Release of Version 2
03/21/2023: Release of Version 2.1

Version 2 Patch Notes:
- Added RMS support
- Corrected the position of obstacles near the bridge, they are now more like they are in real life
- Tweaked the ground pattern to make it look more like it does in real life
- Added pavement to some areas (most importantly next to the rail near the volleyball courts) and fixed the texture mapping in general
- Adjusted some textures
- Added the ground gutter next to the plaza
- Added some hot air balloons to the sky
- Reworked the bridge on the other side of the river
- Made some surfaces brighter during night time

Version 2.1 Patch Notes:
- Adjusted a few textures
- Fixed the bridge's lighting (bridge mesh was too dark / wasn't correctly lit by the sky light) 

Big thanks to Nikkelas for giving me a bunch of suggestions to make this recreation more accurate

I also made an alternate version without the barriers. I didn't plan on removing them so collisions outside of the plaza are gonna be off/weird. Link to the barrier-less verison:

Assets.Name: TunaHighOfficial
Assets.Description:
-- Tuna High  -- Official Release -- 

Custom Day/ Night Cycle - the in-game day night functions wont work and the camera light will need to be turned on and off manually. numbers 1 - 6 will take you to the various times of day from 1 (morning) to 6 (night). "D" key will double the rate of time and the "P" key will pause time. this will need to be done manually except when you pause the game. Benefit is none of this requires pausing, you can set time of day and pause it whenever you want. I would recomend Vato's (Travis Bragg) Camera light controller. it isnt necessary but a nice mod to have. Nighttime is DARK. like real life dark. you will need to light areas to see if they arent lit by the night lights on the map. Thanks to my testers who hopefully helped me get the collisions and such working nicely before upload. ❤️ I'm a dingus so there isnt a thumbnail because i forgot and cant be bothered to reupload for something so small.

Enjoy: 

EDIT: I didnt mention before to make sure you uninstall the older version of tuna or there may be conflicts between the old and new layout.

here is a slight fix for the post processing on the map. if you feel like the contrast is too high or it is too desaturated. i recommend this. install like a regular mod: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1fVaeYVtOfBYSBodiBKtYphQI2NMW9tMi/view?usp=sharing

Assets.Description:
First off, sorry to yap, This is kind of a map release.
* I have very little experience/knowledge in unreal, i apologize for jank.

* I did spend about 40 ish hours learning and testing things, building the map, but i got a huge distraction and shelved it.

* I will likely keep it shelved for a bit... but considering the amount put in and how much i do love it, ill release it as a "beta" 

* Anything with graffiti is a 3d scan of real life locations (the Berlin wall wraps the entire skate space), and the collision is quite complex, try not to collide with them (this is mostly for walls, a few of the 3d scans are skate-able with simpler collision)

Assets.Name: Pipe Dreams
Assets.Description:
Pipe Dreams is an attempt to give us new things to skate that are not always found in Session.  Things like halfpipes, fullpipes, big jumps and a long downhill run.  The other stuff is also included in a lot of spots too.  It has two missions and some secret rewards, and includes a save system, so you can rush off to skate IRL and finish later.  Can you find all 4 Easter eggs?  Track them in the menu.

There are some shadow issues, based on my rudimentary building style in Unreal with brushes and no 3D modeling program.  Those are around buildings A and B roofs(labeled on side) and small rails and pipes all over.  I didn't want to push the map back for just visual issues, and didn't strive for a high quality, instead striving for a high level of fun.  

🚨  If you have any issues deleting your game save in the menu(ONLY DELETES THE PROGRESS IN THE MAP), leaving the map and returning should fix those. 

⭐ I personally use the X2 pump multiplier, though its not a must it helps.  It's located here https://discord.com/channels/612703594134634498/943801815588278292/1340870241948794986

Assets.Name: Customizable_Blank_Decks
Assets.Description:
This mod add 100 deck graphic variants to the blank decks that you can swap with png files or with normal cooked files
YOU NEED TO HAVE THE SESSION BP MOD LOADER INSTALLED FIRSTDeck Sizes
7.25    7.5    7.75     8.0     8.125     8.25     8.5     8.75

For PNG Deck Graphics
add them to Content\CustomDeckGraphics\PNG  and name them  DG_001_TEX - DG_100_TEX


For Cooked Assets 
textures folder path and texture names
CustomDeckGraphics\Textures   DG_001_TEX - DG_100_TEX

materials folder path and material names
CustomDeckGraphics\Materials  DG_001_MAI - DG_100_MAI

icons folder path and icon names 
CustomDeckGraphics\Icons  DG_001_ICON - DG_100_ICON

if you find any issues let me know and ill fix them

Assets.Name: Isaac_Clarke_without_Kinesis
Assets.Description:
🎃 It's officially Spooktober! 🎃
Skate 3's best secret character, **Isaac Clarke from Dead Space**, is now in Session! No cheat code required this time.

There are two versions, the attached file has him without his left hand's Kinesis Module (G.R.I.P.), exactly as he appeared in Skate 3. Further down will be an alternate version with the Kinesis Module included if you want it.

He replaces Ribsman so that you can still customize your board (assuming you're using Chuy's customizable Ribsman mod from here https://discord.com/channels/612703594134634498/1033542578588627015/1222637314484736000)

I couldn't find a model rip of his unique board from Skate 3, so instead I added the Dead Space "Last Stand" deck here: https://discord.com/channels/612703594134634498/943801688513454080/1290568940095012864

Special thanks to <@218805278802444289> and <@1007121558810152990> for helping me with some UE4/Blender quirks!
Assets.Author: akelaphobia#0

Assets.Name: 100_Custom_Object_Dropper_Slots
Assets.Description:
Updated 4/5/2024 

100_Custom_Object_Dropper_Slots
This mod add a new category to the object dropper with 100 empty object slots


Path: Content/ObjectPlacement/CustomObjects/
Folder Names: Object_001 - Object_100
Icon Names: UI_001 - UI_100
Static Mesh Names: SM_001 - SM_100
Blueprint Names: BP_001 - BP_100


Example if you want to make an object for slot 001
01.in ue4 make the path Content/ObjectPlacement/CustomObjects/Object_001

02.in the Object_001 folder add your mesh and icon and properly name them the mesh name should be SM_001 and the icon name should be UI_001 the names of the textures and materials don't matter

03.now just cook your mod and copy over the files to your game

if you want your object 001 to use a custom blueprint make a new actor blueprint and name it BP_001

if you find or have any issues with it let me know

Assets.Name: ClickToCatchBump
Assets.Description:
**TDV_Teleport** (is what it's getting called i guess)

**edited 03/31/2023**

Here's a mod that people have requested i release for a while. 

Press 2 to open a menu that allows you to teleport to :
- Chatham Skateshop (must be on Chatham map)
- Philly Skateshop (must be on Philly map)
- Embarcadero Skateshop (must be on main SFC map)
- China Banks Skateshop (must be on China Banks map)
Press - (minus/dash) to toggle a UI that shows player position and the name of the actor you are currently looking at
Press 0 (zero) to delete the actor in question

**Any objects deleted can be recovered by reloading the map, they are only deleted for the current play session.**

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iEFqeU5XE3tCBqY1s7ob9sYf0mvlPMMB/view?usp=sharingClick to catch and Click to bump out controls

Here's a test for some people who would like to try it
This changes the bump out of lip tricks to stick clicks, also changes manual catch to stick click

Unzip and put the .ini file into "Session/SessionGame/Config"

If you don't like it, just delete the file and no harm done.

3 Variations:
Click to catch only
Click to catch and bump out of grinds
Click to bump out of grinds only** TDV_CharacterSwapper**

Hold RB and A to open the menu.

When a new character is added for it, the character just needs to be installed like any other gear and it will appear in this menu.

And then name your mesh 
SKM_CS_Mesh001 
through
SKM_CS_Mesh050

when posting ur mod, make sure to include which mesh number u replace so others can try to avoid overwriting yours

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Orz39O0XCbDRzfJE71fQkQV48HbUqkxe/view?usp=share_link**Board Break Mod**
preview by <@527585400173363210> 

**Requires chuy's bp loader** located here: https://discord.com/channels/612703594134634498/943801815588278292/1026676949906640977

Press U to open the customization menu for board break settings
-Min airtime is the amount of airtime required before the board will break.
-Break chance is the odds that it will break if the minimum airtime is obtained.
-Random break checkbox disables breaking automatically and it can only be triggered by pressing **\ (Backslash)  or holding RB and pressing B**
-Checkboxes for nose,tail, and middle breaks to enable or disable them for random breaks, or only setting 1 enabled allows repeatedly breaking the same place for recording the board breaking (does not break automatically in replay, must be manually triggered)
-Checkbox for foot position will enable/disable the foot moving tot he position that the board will break (doing a shuv and making the board backwards will break this function, or skating switch without doing a shuv)
